ProtoResult:
. "If $\mathbf{X}$ and $\mathbf{Y}$ are any two vectors in 
   $\R^n$ then $ |\mathbf{X}\cdot\mathbf{Y}|\le |\mathbf{X}| 
   |\mathbf{Y}|, $ with equality if and only if one of the 
   vectors is a scalar multiple of the other."
